sect2.para:
To configure the VPF data, switch to the Debrief tote and select View Layer Manager. The Layer Manager will open, and show our Track:Carpet layer together with another layer, Chart Features. Click on the symbol to the left of the Chart Features (
) text to open that layer, and you will see the following view, clearly showing the new VPF layer.
Layer Manager

entry.para:
Java 3D Libraries (required for viewing Debrief plots in 3D
                        


 To interactively view Debrief plots in 3 dimensions the Java 3d runtime files and libraries must be installed on the machine.  These libraries are a free download from the Java website. 
